node.text: “I'll have a better understanding of why in a year, and an even better one in two, and an even greater one in five, and it'll go from being, you know, a book of my life to becoming a chapter to a paragraph to a line to a word to a doodle.” For the August issue of GQ, Jason Sudeikis opens up to @Zachbaron. Head to the link in bio to read the story and see all the photographs by @hillandaubrey. Styled by @michaeldarlington.
